snippet.title: Sailist - Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Demo Link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1999320/Sailist/

I'm excited to release a demo of the Sailist I've been working on for a long time!
This demo allows you to play with the basics of Sailist without any restrictions.
